    <div class="fr-view">
        <h2  style="text-align: center;">Food waste prevention training</h2><p style="text-align: center;">Whether you&rsquo;re a business, a non-profit or an individual, our food waste prevention workshops give you strategies and tips to maximize your food, save money, and reduce the environmental impact of food waste.&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: left;">Here are the food waste prevention workshops we offer: &nbsp;</p>
    </div>


    








<div class="container-fluid image_text_cta_container squiggly_top white   ">

	<div class="container max_body_width_narrow image_text_cta_inner_container">

		<div class="row">

			<div class="col image_container fade ">
				<div class="frame default"></div>
				<img src="/SecondHarvest/media/Images/Get%20Involved/athome-bbd.jpg" class="fade w_left_offset" alt="People reading a jam jar" />
			</div>

			<div class="col text_container ml-auto">
				<div class="text_inner_container fade w_margin_offset">

							<h3>Food Date Labelling</h3>
						<div class="green_underline small"></div>
				
					<span class="text"><p >This one-hour interactive workshop is designed to clear up the confusion about expiry and best before dates, a major cause of food waste in Canada.  &nbsp;</p><p>Here&rsquo;s what you&rsquo;ll learn: &nbsp;</p><ul><li>How to tell the difference between various date label terms &nbsp;</li><li>How to know when food is good or not good to eat &nbsp;</li><li>How to reduce food waste at home&nbsp;</li><li>How date labels contribute to unnecessary food waste in Canada   &nbsp;</li></ul></span>

						<a href="/resources/training/training-request-form" target="" class="rounded_button auto_width extra_side_padding default" aria-label="Food Date Labelling Request a training">Request a training</a>
					
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>

	</div>

</div>


    








<div class="container-fluid image_text_cta_container squiggly_top white alternate_image   ">

	<div class="container max_body_width_narrow image_text_cta_inner_container">

		<div class="row">

			<div class="col image_container fade ">
				<div class="frame green_bg"></div>
				<img src="/SecondHarvest/media/Images/Resources/fwp-elearning.jpg" class="fade w_left_offset" alt="Person holding milk" />
			</div>

			<div class="col text_container ml-auto">
				<div class="text_inner_container fade w_margin_offset">

							<h3>A Guide to Food Date Labelling</h3>
						<div class="green_underline small"></div>
				
					<span class="text"><p >This self-paced option provides all the information of the live food date labelling workshop at your own schedule.  &nbsp;</p><p>Here&rsquo;s what you&rsquo;ll learn: &nbsp;</p><ul><li>How to tell the difference between the various date label terms &nbsp;</li><li>How to know when food is good or not good to eat &nbsp;</li><li>How to reduce food waste at home&nbsp;</li><li>How date labels contribute to unnecessary food waste in Canada  &nbsp;</li></ul></span>

						<a href="https://training.secondharvest.ca/course/view.php?id=2" target="_blank" class="rounded_button auto_width extra_side_padding default" aria-label="A Guide to Food Date Labelling Take the training">Take the training</a>
					
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>

	</div>

</div>


    








<div class="container-fluid image_text_cta_container squiggly_top white   ">

	<div class="container max_body_width_narrow image_text_cta_inner_container">

		<div class="row">

			<div class="col image_container fade ">
				<div class="frame orange_bg"></div>
				<img src="/SecondHarvest/media/Images/Resources/fwp-elearning2.jpg" class="fade w_left_offset" alt="Person holding food in a crate" />
			</div>

			<div class="col text_container ml-auto">
				<div class="text_inner_container fade w_margin_offset">

							<h3>A Donor Guide to Food Recovery</h3>
						<div class="green_underline small"></div>
				
					<span class="text"><p >This self-paced learning gives businesses the information and tools they need to start donating their surplus food or improve their rescue practices.</p><p>Here&rsquo;s what you&rsquo;ll learn: &nbsp;</p><ul><li>The impact of food waste in Canada&nbsp;</li><li>Common misconceptions about donating food&nbsp;</li><li>What you need to know to make regular food donations to your community</li></ul></span>

						<a href="https://training.secondharvest.ca/course/view.php?id=3" target="_blank" class="rounded_button auto_width extra_side_padding default" aria-label="A Donor Guide to Food Recovery Take the training">Take the training</a>
					
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>

	</div>

</div>


    








<div class="container-fluid image_text_cta_container squiggly_top white alternate_image   ">

	<div class="container max_body_width_narrow image_text_cta_inner_container">

		<div class="row">

			<div class="col image_container fade ">
				<div class="frame default"></div>
