			</div>

			<div class="col text_container ml-auto">
				<div class="text_inner_container fade w_margin_offset">

							<h3>Food Storage</h3>
						<div class="green_underline small"></div>
				
					<span class="text"><p >This one-hour interactive workshop is designed to explore food storage best practices to maximize food&rsquo;s lifespan.&nbsp;</p><p>Here&rsquo;s what you&rsquo;ll learn:&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Best practices on how to store specific food items to prevent spoilage&nbsp;</li><li>Industry tips for maximizing food at home or in commercial kitchens&nbsp;</li><li>How food is unnecessarily wasted in Canada &nbsp;</li></ul></span>

						<a href="/resources/training/training-request-form" target="" class="rounded_button auto_width extra_side_padding default" aria-label="Food Storage Request a training">Request a training</a>
					
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>

	</div>

</div>


    








<div class="container-fluid image_text_cta_container squiggly_top white   ">

	<div class="container max_body_width_narrow image_text_cta_inner_container">

