			<div class="col image_container fade ">
				<div class="frame green_bg"></div>
				<img src="/SecondHarvest/media/Images/Resources/fwp-audits.jpg" class="fade w_left_offset" alt="Person weighing food" />
			</div>

			<div class="col text_container ml-auto">
				<div class="text_inner_container fade w_margin_offset">

							<h3>Food Waste Audit</h3>
						<div class="green_underline small"></div>
				
					<span class="text"><p >This one-hour interactive workshop is designed to teach you how to do a food waste audit and revolutionize food spaces. You can&rsquo;t change what you don&rsquo;t know, so measure your food waste to reduce it! &nbsp;</p><p>Here&rsquo;s what you&rsquo;ll learn: &nbsp;</p><ul><li>Why food waste audits are important &nbsp;</li><li>How to complete a simple food waste audit &nbsp;</li><li>Tips for developing an impactful food waste reduction action plan&nbsp;</li><li>An understanding of the environmental impacts of food waste</li></ul></span>

						<a href="/resources/training/training-request-form" target="" class="rounded_button auto_width extra_side_padding default" aria-label="Food Waste Audit Request a training">Request a training</a>
					
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>

	</div>

</div>


    








