						<div class="green_underline small"></div>
				
					<span class="text"><p >We&rsquo;ve developed a set of engaging workshops for teams and corporate groups who want to understand the issues of food waste and loss and build skills to reduce their individual impact on the environment.</p><p>You&rsquo;ve got options! Here are the corporate workshops on food waste prevention we offer: </p><ul><li>Food Waste and Date Labels </li><li>Food Waste Reduction for Households </li><li>Hands-on Food Waste Reduction for Households </li><li>Food Waste Audit Challenge </li></ul><p>Review the full details of our <a href="/getmedia/06344465-8e14-47d0-8e31-cb26538ba9e4/SH-Training-Opportunities-for-Corporates.pdf" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">corporate training programs</a>.</p></span>

